cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a new loss function for training neural network classifiers that focuses on building useful representations by encouraging natural clustering within the latent space. As such, it is likely to be relevant to several sub-categories within computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
